verbose_text: Our results demonstrated the mechanism of the circNCX1/miR-133a-3p/CDIP1 regulatory pathway, in which circNCX1 acts as a miR-133a-3p sponge by inhibiting the regulation of miR-133a-3p on CDIP1.
